item.title: By: Daddyo
item.dc:creator: Daddyo
item.description: Can you do text over the phone, too? Not much to say, and a picture is worth a thousand words. Good thing you were'nt in DC for the fireworks. Everybody had to be evacuated into the museums, and then were let out for the fireworks. A bunch of people were hurt by fireworks in Vienna, VA.
